    <!-- 
        Narrative Plan:
        1. Hero Section: Hook the viewer with a strong title and key stats (total publications, years of experience).
        2. Skills Showcase: Visually break down core competencies using donut charts to represent proficiency and focus.
        3. Career Journey: A vertical timeline to clearly display professional progression from research to industry.
        4. Publication Timeline: A bar chart to visualize research output over the years, showing consistency and dedication.
        5. Academic Foundation & Awards: Conclude by reinforcing expertise with education credentials and notable awards in styled cards.

        Color Palette: Energetic & Playful (#00A6ED, #003554, #051923, #FF6600, #FFB400)

        Visualization Choices:
        - Big Numbers (Hero): Goal: Inform. Method: Styled HTML. Justification: High impact, immediate communication of key metrics.
        - Donut Charts (Skills): Goal: Compare/Inform. Method: Chart.js Canvas. Justification: Visually represents the composition of her skillset.
        - Vertical Timeline (Experience): Goal: Change. Method: Structured HTML/CSS. Justification: Best non-SVG method to show chronological progression.
        - Bar Chart (Publications): Goal: Change/Compare. Method: Chart.js Canvas. Justification: Effectively compares publication counts across years.
        - Styled Cards (Education/Awards): Goal: Organize/Inform. Method: Styled HTML. Justification: Clean, modern way to present lists of achievements.

        Constraint Confirmation: NO SVG graphics or Mermaid JS are used in this document. All charts are rendered on Canvas elements.
    -->

